+        • (HyperNetworkInterface, FOPNGPlus)  — FOPNG+ for hypernetworks
+        • (DirectModelInterface,  FOPNG)      — FOPNG for plain MLP / CNN
+        • (DirectModelInterface,  FOPNGPlus)  — FOPNG+ for plain MLP / CNN
